How to use?

# Windows only

# download server files
http://github.com/X13home/x13home.github.io/archive/bin_Server.zip
unpack x13home.github.io-bin_Server.zip

copy file 
    from x13home.github.io-bin_Client\bin
    to   x13home.github.io-bin_Server\bin 

cd x13home.github.io-bin_Server\bin

###########################################################################

If you want use embedded engine

Start client:
    CC.exe

At the first start, select the 1st item: Embedded Engine

###########################################################################

If you want install local server as service

Start client as Administartor:
    CC.exe

At the first start, select second item: Install Engine as service.

###########################################################################

If you want use local server as application

Start server:
    engine.exe

Start client:
    CC.exe

At the first start, select the last item.
Don't change the URL, user name and password.
Must be:
    URL:        Localhost
    username:   local
    password:

###########################################################################

If you want use another server.

Start client:
    CC.exe

At the first start, select the last item.
URL: Enter server IP or name.
Select user name: root
password shown in server directory, file data\security.xst, 
         record <item name="root" value="password here"...../>
